{"tid":586659,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★愛\"奴動\"福音！統計處：85歲長者仍要工作 日做12小時","createTime":"2018-03-09T17:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T08:37:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd982723a967561c630b831780b1b8ce7f7c5fa1","tid":586659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:12:05.000Z","msg":"65歲講退休或許已成過去式！根據統計處最新出版的《2016年中期人口統計主題性報告：長者》顯示，長者工作人口在06年至16年期間，由約5.9萬人，急增逾一倍至約12.5萬人，主要受65至74歲的年齡組別所帶動，由約4.7萬急升至11.2萬人。<br />\n<br />\n而更值得留意的是，有近400名、85歲或以上的長者仍要工作。在長者工作人口中，並非是過日辰的「風流工」，約5萬名長者每周工作45小時或以上，以6日計，即每日工作7.5小時。當中有逾5600名長者，更要日做近12小時，不禁令人聞者心酸。<br />\n<br />\n另外，新一代長者教育程度逐漸改善，長者中擁有中學或以上教育程度的比例由25%顯著上升至2016年的39.6%。長者擁有專上教育程度的比例亦由6.6%上升至9.5%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/bkn-20180309174910576-0309_00822_001.html?refer=hn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180309%2Fbkn-20180309174910576-0309_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn&d=uD6lAQA5miGWf9rW1QZJszACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=3b123add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180309/bkn-20180309174910576-0309_00822_001.html?refer=hn</a>"},{"pid":"9a73910e6e6f365d78e8086b4f17cc959bc31ae7","tid":586659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabcd8385e4e7fde31c9ad6bdcdf672d0ab0ad06","tid":586659,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a73910e6e6f365d78e8086b4f17cc959bc31ae7","tid":586659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T17:14:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab91a57fd8e8ec04ea836c5053b5ed7bbdbda141","tid":586659,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s